shon]]\n* [[Jake Gyllenhaal]]\n* [[Maggie Gyllenhaal]]\n* [[Felicity Huffman]]\n* [[Jidenna]]<ref name=\"LAT How celebrities\">{{cite news |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-et-ent-celebrity-womens-march-message-trump-20170123-story.html |title=How celebrities at the Women's March say they'll reflect the change they want to see in America |website=Los Angeles Times |last=Woerner |first=Meredith |date=January 23, 2017 |accessdate=January 25, 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124202629/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-et-ent-celebrity-womens-march-message-trump-20170123-story.html |archivedate=January 24, 2017 }}</ref>\n* [[Scarlett Johansson]]\n* [[Leslie Jones (comedian)|Leslie Jones]]\n* [[Joshua Kushner]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/times2/a-tale-of-two-brothers-one-in-trumps-team-the-other-on-a-protest-march-sg2c7rqzq |title=A tale of two brothers \u2013 one in Trump's team, the other on a protest march |website=The Times |last1=Rumbelow |first=Helen |date=January 24, 2017 |accessdate=January 26, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Padma Lakshmi]]<ref name=\"People Laksmi\">{{cite news |url=http://people.com/celebrity/padma-lakshmi-adam-dell-womens-march-drew-barrymore-will-kopelman |title=Padma Lakshmi Marches with Ex Adam Dell and Their Daughter After Reports They Rekindled Romance |author=Dave Quinn |date=January 22, 2017 |website=People |accessdate=January 25, 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124190737/http://people.com/celebrity/padma-lakshmi-adam-dell-womens-march-drew-barrymore-will-kopelman/ |archivedate=January 24, 2017 }}</ref>\n* [[Brie Larson]]\n* [[Natasha Lyonne]]\n* [[Macklemore]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/reliable-source/wp/2017/01/22/an-abundance-of-performers-and-pussyhats-at-womens-march-after-party/ |title=An abundance of performers and pussyhats at Women's March after-party |author=Sarah Polus |date=January 22, 2017 |web